title: Start
body:
Jenny: Jake is watching TV shows at living room while grandma is not convenience in preparing food.

		Jenny: Should I help grandma to prepare food?

		[[I should help Grandma to prepare lunch since she has walking difficulties.|HelpGrandma]]

		[[I want to watch my favourite show on TV with Jake.|NothelpGrandma]]

title: HelpGrandma
body: Grandma is happy and we are ready to have a nice and delicious lunch.

title: NothelpGrandma
body: Jenny: Oh no! Grandma had difficulties serving the food and spilled it!
